01:25:36.771 --> 01:25:38.851
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Sempre se lastimando</b></c>

01:25:39.231 --> 01:25:41.110
<font color=#FFFF00><b>e enchendo o saco de todo mundo.</b></c>

01:25:41.111 --> 01:25:43.628
<font color=#FFFF00><b>O maior erro dela
