01:25:43.629 --> 01:25:45.571
<font color=#FFFF00><b>com esse imbecil de merda.</b></c>

01:25:46.971 --> 01:25:48.271
<font color=#FFFF00><b>O quê?</b></c>

01:25:49.870 --> 01:25:51.170
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Nada.</b></c>

01:25:51.171 --> 01:25:54.471
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Não seja covarde, filho.
