01:28:52.771 --> 01:28:55.989
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Ela chupa o pau daquele fracassado!</b></c>

01:28:55.990 --> 01:28:57.290
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Willis.</i></b></c>

01:28:57.291 --> 01:28:58.990
<font color=#FFFF00><b>- Me mate, então!
<i>- Willis.</i></b></c>

01:28:58.991 --> 01:29:01.030
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Me mate, maldito chupador de pau!</b></c>

01:29:01.031 --> 01:29:02.331
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Chega!</b></c>

01:29:02.870 --> 01:29:04.170
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Pare, Willis.</i></b></c>

01:29:04.171 --> 01:29:05.471
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Gwen!</b></c>

