01:29:07.331 --> 01:29:09.170
<font color=#FFFF00><b>- Gwen.
<i>- Willis.</i></b></c>

01:29:09.171 --> 01:29:10.471
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Gwen!</b></c>

01:29:12.251 --> 01:29:13.850
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Papai, por favor.</b></c>

01:29:13.851 --> 01:29:15.250
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Willis.</i></b></c>

01:29:15.251 --> 01:29:16.650
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Calma.</b></c>

01:29:16.651 --> 01:29:17.951
<font color=#FFFF00><b><i>Willis.</i></b></c>

01:29:23.171 --> 01:29:24.890
<font color=#FFFF00><b>- Pronto.
- Não, não, não.</b></c>

01:29:24.891 --> 01:29:27.771
<font color=#FFFF00><b>- Acabou, papai.
