<font color=#FFFF00><b>Sim, senhor.</b></c>

01:31:41.411 --> 01:31:43.196
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Bom dia, filho.</b></c>

01:31:49.791 --> 01:31:52.371
<font color=#FFFF00><b>Pelo amor de Deus!</b></c>

